{"tid":35444,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈譴責IVE學生借LIHKG報私怨","createTime":"2016-12-12T05:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T11:31:21.000Z","uid":7775,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"260032bc46ebdc26ca65ee8a54b448c1e701941f","tid":35444,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有人開post 重提仙氣女神一事<br />\n<br />\n並講出仙氣而家正在同阿sir拍拖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7yyU0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7yyU0P.jpg&h=97c5c5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巧合地，一呼百應，即刻有人留言話睇佢唔順眼，並且提出好嚴重既指控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AFj0p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AFj0p6.jpg&h=86f280b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/133118_7a26f9dc765ff91b6cbe456096b31d17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F133118_7a26f9dc765ff91b6cbe456096b31d17.jpg&h=a96e65d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但無提及任何證據證明佢地任何指控<br />\n即使巴打們追問仍不得要領<br />\n<br />\n依位仲搞笑，一開始玩人格謀殺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYGLotf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYGLotf.jpg&h=1bca8cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我提出質疑，佢就話自己係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/133356_ad28004928df6ae5c368a78a91c24afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F133356_ad28004928df6ae5c368a78a91c24afc.jpg&h=b466c68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾有人都承認自己因爲人地同3個男既一組做project，唔妥人，但留言間仍毫無悔意<br />\n<br />\n當我求下你地班IVE學生，唔好污染、做臭連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇到最近好多亂咁起底、狙擊人既post<br />\n<br />\n亦都覺得有需要出聲正視問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8372f649365bc576d7de6f367cf0436525a998ec","tid":35444,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔提都唔記得佢"},{"pid":"55bf9adc63cf5a56641e7e6773fc6f0c4ca37ffe","tid":35444,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/34755/page/9?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/34755/page/9?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n補圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QV0X2E8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV0X2E8.jpg&h=3eaa207f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2651cb856b935d4c8f7a2311b8d6e4f26b35ba11","tid":35444,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"我認為係一班ive妹唔抵得人、圍爐杯人<br />\n<br />\n跟住一班想埋堆既做應聲蟲幫手屌、借論壇攻擊人"},{"pid":"7311d3fd188d1300131cb504922782055d25f03d","tid":35444,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e513896dd3a13a17cc393152ff67f149789b7ee","tid":35444,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmh"},{"pid":"a10f6f88023f7858733b3cac8fb8def81d2e980b","tid":35444,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"希望有人可以提供到果班野既資料<br />\n<br />\n例如whatsapp group對話紀錄證明<br />\n<br />\n來源保證會保密<br />\n<br />\n識我既都知，有資料我係一定會玩真"},{"pid":"ee0188f9e305a9b35bf35fa2200283484cc79edb","tid":35444,"uid":20180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"好心IVE仔就專心讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src